  "title": "Partial Order",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "A binary relation $R$ on $A$ is a \\textbf{partial order} if it is reflexive,\nantisymmetric, and transitive.\nA set $A$ equipped with a partial order $R$ is a \\textbf{partially ordered set}\nor \\textbf{poset}, written $(A,R)$.",
